content.c_answer2: The complete London cast includes Alexia Khadime (Elphaba), Lucy St. Louis (Glinda), Ryan Reid (Fiyero), Sophie\-Louise Dann (Madame Morrible), Mark Curry (The Wizard), Caitlin Anderson (Nessarose), Joe Thompson\-Oubari (Boq), and Simeon Truby (Doctor Dillamond).
